24 (a) technological equipment enhancements and expansions considered by the trustees to support
25 enhanced educational programs in the classroom;
26 (b) facility expansion and remodeling considered by the trustees to support the delivery of
27 educational programs, to address health or safety hazards, or to support the removal and replacement of
28 obsolete facilities;
